{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Dear players and adventurers:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>We are a small group of independent game developers. We are trying to make independent games in some different ways.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Although we have experienced some hardships and our development speed is limited, we are still working hard.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>You are welcome to leave messages in various ways and tell us your thoughts and opinions about this game.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>We will take seriously every player's suggestions, ideas, and even complaints. All of them have extremely high value and are important bases and references for our iterative updates.</strong><br> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/1y.png?t=1735999361\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/1.gif?t=1735999361\" /><strong>Create the ultimate 2D pixel-based battle experience in the name of ACT!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/2y.png?t=1735999361\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/2.gif?t=1735999361\" /><strong>This world provides a variety of combinations of weapons and skills, each of which can bring different strategies and combat experiences.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>At the same time, it also combines the characteristics of horizontal action games to create secrets for this world.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088410/extras/3y.png